      • onMissing

        public Route.AssetDefinition onMissing(int statusCode)
        Indicates what to do when an asset is missing (not resolved). Default action is to resolve them as 404 (NOT FOUND) request. If you specify a status code <= 0, missing assets are ignored and the next handler on pipeline will be executed.
        Parameters:
        statusCode - HTTP code or 0.
        Returns:
        This route definition.

      • maxAge

        public Route.AssetDefinition maxAge(String maxAge)
        Parse value as Duration. If the value is already a number then it uses as seconds. Otherwise, it parse expressions like: 8m, 1h, 365d, etc...
        Parameters:
        maxAge - Set the cache header max-age value in seconds.
        Returns:
